      <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></div><h3>24/7 Available</h3><p>Round-the-clock service for airport pickups, late-night returns, and emergency travel.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-rupee-sign"></i></div><h3>Transparent Pricing</h3><p>No hidden charges. Fixed packages and clear per-km rates. What you see is what you pay.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i></div><h3>Live Tracking</h3><p>Track your cab's live location from booking confirmation till arrival. Full transparency.</p></div>
    </div>
